Returns a Watcher which notifies its listeners when the result of the given Query becomes available or changes. e.g: Watcher<Object> watcher = client.fileWatcher("foo", "bar", Query.identity("/baz.json")); watcher.watch((revision, content) -> { JsonNode json = (JsonNode) content; ... });
fileWatcher(String, String, Query<T>, Function<? super T, ? extends U>) - Method in interface com.linecorp.centraldogma.client.CentralDogma
